OL,3,CBurnham: Labour would 'do well to
OL,4,Clisten to' Rayner after criticism of PM
OL,6,FGreater Manchester mayor Andy Burnham
OL,7,Fhas backed Angela Rayner after her
OL,8,Fcriticism of Labour under Sir Keir
OL,9,FStarmer's leadership.
OL,11,FIn a speech on Tuesday night, the
OL,12,Fformer deputy prime minister warned
OL,13,Fthe party is "running out of time" to
OL,14,Fdeliver the change they promised -
OL,15,Fwith the "survival" of the party at
OL,16,Fstake.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
