OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773921770
OL,3,CBurnham: Labour would 'do well to
OL,4,Clisten to' Rayner after criticism of PM
OL,6,FSpeaking on Wednesday morning, Burnham
OL,7,Fexpressed support for Rayner's
OL,8,Fcomments, telling BBC Radio 4 that his
OL,9,Fparty would "do well to listen to what
OL,10,FAngela has got to say."
OL,12,FRayner - who served as Keir Starmer's
OL,13,Fdeputy until she resigned in September
OL,14,F2025 - also hit out at the
OL,15,Fgovernment's flagship immigration
OL,16,Freforms, calling them "un-British" and
OL,17,Fa "breach of trust".
OL,26,@rD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
