OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773921770
OL,3,CBurnham: Labour would 'do well to
OL,4,Clisten to' Rayner after criticism of PM
OL,6,F"I certainly know where she's coming
OL,7,Ffrom," Burnham said. "We've got to,
OL,8,Fall of us, haven't we, work together
OL,9,Fto pull together a plan that turns the
OL,10,Fcountry around.
OL,12,F"I understand the frustration people
OL,13,Ffeel. We heard that at the by-
OL,14,Felection, and of course, Angela is
OL,15,Freflecting some of that."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
