OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773921770
OL,3,CBurnham: Labour would 'do well to
OL,4,Clisten to' Rayner after criticism of PM
OL,6,FThe comments come as Starmer has faced
OL,7,Fpressure to shift his policy platform
OL,8,Fto the left following Labour's defeat
OL,9,Fat the hands of the Green Party in the
OL,10,FGorton and Denton by-election earlier
OL,11,Fthis month.
OL,13,FIn her most significant intervention
OL,14,Fsince leaving government, Rayner said
OL,15,Fproposals to double the time it takes
OL,16,Fmigrants to qualify for permanently
OL,17,Fresidence in the UK "pull the rug"
OL,18,Ffrom those who are "contributing to
OL,19,Four economy and to our society".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
