OL,3,CBurnham: Labour would 'do well to
OL,4,Clisten to' Rayner after criticism of PM
OL,6,FThe Home Secretary Shabana Mahmood has
OL,7,Fannounced plans to double the time it
OL,8,Ftakes for migrants to qualify for
OL,9,Fpermanent residence from five to ten
OL,10,Fyears, arguing that long-term
OL,11,Fsettlement is a "privilege" that must
OL,12,Fbe earned.
OL,14,FThe reforms are also set to stipulate
OL,15,Fthat tougher requirements, such as
OL,16,Fspeaking English to a higher standard,
OL,17,Fwill also need to be met in order for
OL,18,Fmigrants stay in Britain.
OL,26,@sD@QOUsD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
