OL,3,CBurnham: Labour would 'do well to
OL,4,Clisten to' Rayner after criticism of PM
OL,6,FShe has since been widely seen as a
OL,7,Fpotential successor to Sir Keir amid
OL,8,Frumblings of a leadership challenge as
OL,9,Fboth Labour's poll ratings and the
OL,10,Fprime minister's personal approval
OL,11,Fflounder.
