OL,3,CBurnham: Labour would 'do well to
OL,4,Clisten to' Rayner after criticism of PM
OL,6,FCabinet Minister Nick Thomas-Symonds
OL,7,Ftold ITV News that what he called
OL,8,FRayner's "impatience to deliver
OL,9,Fchange" is shared across government,
OL,10,Fadding that she made an "excellent
OL,11,Fcontribution to government".
OL,13,F"In terms of the impatience that I
OL,14,Fthink is running through not just her
OL,15,Fremarks but what I hear from voters on
OL,16,Fa weekly basis, that impatience to
OL,17,Fdeliver change is exactly what is
OL,18,Fshared right across government by all
OL,19,Fministers," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
